### 创建兑换订单
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/exchange/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1

{
  "orderType": "BUY_CRYPTO",
  "fiatCurrency": "USD",
  "cryptoCurrency": "BTC",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "paymentMethod": "ALIPAY",
  "walletAddress": "1A1zP1eP5QGefi2DMPTfTL5SLmv7DivfNa",
  "autoExecute": true,
  "remark": "测试订单"
}

### 获取订单详情
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/exchange/orders/EX1234567890
X-User-ID: 1

### 获取用户订单列表
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/exchange/orders?status=PENDING
X-User-ID: 1

### 取消订单
DELETE http://localhost:8084/api/v1/exchange/orders/EX1234567890
X-User-ID: 1

### 获取实时价格
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/prices/BTC-USD

### 获取加权平均价格
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/prices/weighted/BTC/USD

### 计算兑换汇率
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/prices/exchange-rate?fromCurrency=USD&toCurrency=BTC&amount=1000

### 获取价格变化
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/prices/BTC-USD/change?hours=24

### 支付回调（模拟）
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/exchange/payment/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

paymentOrderNo=PAY1234567890&status=SUCCESS&transactionId=TX1234567890 